Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.77,0:00:05.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Raise your eyes you can see\Nshooting stars up in the night sky
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.40,0:00:13.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Raise your eyes you can see\Nshooting stars up in the night sky
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.69,0:00:33.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,One, two...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.44,0:00:36.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The sound resonates\NInto my heart, so hard and deep
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.39,0:00:40.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A field of stars spans endlessly\NAnd through it I carve a passageway
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.35,0:00:42.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,In step with time as generations change
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.39,0:00:44.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Close your eyes and listen closely
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.39,0:00:47.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Shooting stars stream on silently…\Nuntil the goodbye
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.39,0:00:50.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Keep the light inside of you,\Nnever give up don't ever lose
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.39,0:00:52.23,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Transcend time and you will prove,\Nthere is a special place for you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.27,0:00:54.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A blaze of glory is there,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.06,0:00:55.90,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's all a part of our estate;\Nlife is our story to create
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.85,0:01:01.73,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Raise your eyes you can see\Nshooting stars up in the night sky
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.77,0:01:05.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wishes speak from ages old by voice of light\NThroughout the age, never fade away
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.69,0:01:09.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A secret fire, a scream of light,\Nvoices calling through twilight
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.40,0:01:11.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Cast your thoughts to the wind,\Nhang your wishes on the moon
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.52,0:01:13.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Live your life with all your strength\Nfor dreams will reach you very soon
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.48,0:01:16.81,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Raise your eyes you can see\Nshooting stars up in the night sky
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.06,0:01:19.23,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wishes speak from ages old\Nby voice of light
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.27,0:01:21.23,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Throughout the age,\Nnever fade away
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.39,0:01:24.77,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Someday your dream will find\Nits place somewhere
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.81,0:01:28.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Keep shining like a star
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.37,0:01:37.01,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh…!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.24,0:01:42.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.58,0:01:43.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What time is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.05,0:01:47.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad, Big Brother!\NIt's nine already!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.50,0:01:49.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,N-No!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.24,0:01:51.01,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Come on! Bonnie!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.86,0:02:15.33,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hah! Good girl, Bonnie!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.58,0:02:19.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But we don't have time today!\NHurry and let me ride you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.24,0:02:25.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it! You're running away?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.75,0:02:30.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Who's running away?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.15,0:02:31.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Dandelion!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.39,0:02:34.73,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We'll settle this\Nfor sure tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.73,0:02:37.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So you just wait there until then!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.03,0:02:41.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Now don't you go floating\Naway like cotton!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.63,0:02:43.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.09,0:02:43.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.71,0:02:47.27,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Cut the crap! That's my--!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.88,0:02:58.37,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,They're gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.24,0:03:03.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That was a disaster… I'm speechless.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.29,0:03:09.33,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! Just who the hell is he?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.12,0:03:27.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if Jidanbo is all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.71,0:03:29.98,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The wound has closed up, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.56,0:03:32.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Big-bodied men have lots of stamina.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.86,0:03:36.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure he'll be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.33,0:03:37.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.58,0:03:41.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He's so big and so strong.\NI'm sure he'll be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.24,0:03:48.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Still… Who is this Kukaku Shiba\Nwe're going to meet now?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.18,0:03:53.69,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yoruichi never gives us any details…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.93,0:03:55.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's probably someone he knows
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.56,0:03:59.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,who can get us to Seireitei without\Npassing through the gates, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.96,0:04:02.73,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Probably, someone who is\Nfamous for his skill.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.96,0:04:08.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! It must be a cat with\Npedigree papers!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.38,0:04:09.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Like a Persian cat…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.67,0:04:13.79,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Or an American Short Hair…\Nor a Dalmatian.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.33,0:04:15.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Inoue…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.66,0:04:20.41,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't mean it'll be a cat just\Nbecause Yoruichi knows him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.33,0:04:22.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Also…a Dalmatian…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.58,0:04:24.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,is a dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.25,0:04:26.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A dog?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.58,0:04:30.11,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Judging from the name,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.11,0:04:33.66,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,he's probably a well-built man,\Nsomeone like a samurai.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.80,0:04:36.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No, he'll be an old hermit-type master.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.82,0:04:38.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.58,0:04:45.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,See? Like this and this and…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.07,0:04:51.37,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Done!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.60,0:04:55.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A hermit-like macho samurai with cat ears,\Nand a tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.39,0:04:56.94,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No doubt about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.94,0:04:58.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I can't tell what you drew…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.62,0:05:03.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Then how about a skinny\Nguitar-wielding samurai?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.03,0:05:06.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You don't understand, Inoue.\NHe has to have a cape.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.47,0:05:08.27,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh shucks!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.84,0:05:12.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But Kurosaki is late.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.24,0:05:14.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Shall I call him?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.39,0:05:16.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'll go see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.45,0:05:22.12,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, I have to think up\Nthe next Kukaku Shiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.16,0:05:26.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No…you don't have to think.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.04,0:05:27.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.54,0:05:29.90,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.33,0:05:31.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Not going?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.51,0:05:34.60,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Not "not going."\NJust go on ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.96,0:05:38.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to finish the fight with\Nthat guy from yesterday!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.16,0:05:39.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.25,0:05:41.99,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Quit joking around…and come!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.66,0:05:44.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.89,0:05:47.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He'll think I ran away!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.29,0:05:48.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.87,0:05:50.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.18,0:05:52.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't we going yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.24,0:05:53.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Inoue!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.60,0:05:57.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Help me drag this fool\Naway from here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.31,0:05:59.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,W-Who's the fool?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.00,0:06:00.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna beat him up quickly\Nas soon as he shows up,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.88,0:06:02.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,and I'll come after you,\Nso go on--!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.47,0:06:16.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Has blood gone to your head and\Nmade you forget your purpose here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.92,0:06:18.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.88,0:06:21.90,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Rukia's life depends on this journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.90,0:06:24.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Surely, you haven't forgotten.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.35,0:06:29.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You can't waste time just to\Nsee who's more stubborn!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.12,0:06:32.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If you understand, get ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.28,0:06:48.69,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What is it...Renji?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.75,0:06:52.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Did they move up my execution date?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.87,0:06:56.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's less than 14 days to the execution.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.23,0:06:59.66,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The use of Sokyoku has\Nbeen granted.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.41,0:07:03.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're being transferred to Shishinro,\NRepentance Cell.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.83,0:07:14.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.12,0:07:18.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like we've come to\Nthe edge of a village.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.53,0:07:20.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure this is the right way?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.70,0:07:22.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.88,0:07:25.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! According to\Nthe map the Elder gave us,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.95,0:07:27.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,it's supposed to be around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.24,0:07:31.66,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If you have any complaints,\Nyou take the lead!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.04,0:07:34.73,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm not complaining.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.73,0:07:39.27,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kukaku Shiba probably wants\Nto keep his identity a secret,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.27,0:07:41.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,that's why he lives in a place like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.47,0:07:43.90,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately, that is not the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.10,0:07:48.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's just that person's nature…\Nand personal preference.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.40,0:07:51.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.45,0:07:53.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This person moves around quite a bit,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.67,0:07:56.37,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,but the house is always built the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.78,0:07:59.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Once you see it, you’ll recognize it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.83,0:08:01.33,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Once you see it, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.47,0:08:03.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, yes. Just once…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.33,0:08:12.73,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.99,0:08:14.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.78,0:08:16.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wha--!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.47,0:08:17.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.58,0:08:19.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! How neat!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.14,0:08:24.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kukaku Shiba
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.24,0:08:26.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,See? You can recognize it at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.64,0:08:30.89,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's not the problem anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.98,0:08:34.12,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wants to keep his identity a secret?\NThat's probably a lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.36,0:08:36.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He's probably not allowed to live\Nin town
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.47,0:08:38.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,because he builds houses like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.37,0:08:40.33,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's gotta be it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.57,0:08:44.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm… So this time, it's human arms\Nholding the banner.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.79,0:08:46.69,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's pretty neatly done.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.24,0:08:48.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Each time…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.38,0:08:49.53,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He changes the motif?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.41,0:08:51.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.95,0:08:53.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.33,0:09:03.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Argh…we're going to that\Nembarrassing house right now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.91,0:09:07.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to be seen walking\Ninto a house like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.24,0:09:09.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter? Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.71,0:09:10.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.71,0:09:10.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.97,0:09:17.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Ishida! I know you don't\Nwant to go, but hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.44,0:09:18.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.21,0:09:26.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's that chimney?\NIt's awfully big compared to the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.89,0:09:32.33,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like the opening is closed up.\NWhat the…?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.87,0:09:35.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.31,0:09:35.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.02,0:09:37.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Who goes there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.12,0:09:42.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Strangers!\NAnd one is a Soul Reaper!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.29,0:09:47.89,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Suspicious characters!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.89,0:09:49.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I, Koganehiko…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.25,0:09:50.77,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And Shiroganehiko…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.78,0:09:53.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,will not allow you to pass!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.78,0:09:53.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,will not allow you to pass!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.33,0:09:55.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Be gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.86,0:09:59.04,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Or you'll die right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.28,0:10:01.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! Not gatekeepers again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.52,0:10:04.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What a pain this Soul Society is!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.30,0:10:06.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.30,0:10:06.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.24,0:10:10.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Master Yoruichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.10,0:10:16.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A descending stairway\Nas soon as you enter?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.46,0:10:18.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This house really is weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.30,0:10:21.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder how you get upstairs?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.72,0:10:23.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Please pardon us!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.83,0:10:26.90,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We did not know it was you,\NYoruichi, and your companions.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.90,0:10:28.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Please forgive our rudeness.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.86,0:10:30.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We're not his companions.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.45,0:10:34.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's all right. It's my fault\Nfor not notifying you beforehand.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.91,0:10:38.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you! Such generous words\Nfrom such a great personage!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.98,0:10:42.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Please wait here a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.62,0:10:44.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.65,0:10:51.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, right away…Master Kukaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.74,0:11:05.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while, Yoruichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.45,0:11:06.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,K-Kukaku is…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.56,0:11:08.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A woman?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.56,0:11:08.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A woman?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.29,0:11:12.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I never said it was a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.58,0:11:13.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.30,0:11:15.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Who are those kids?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.33,0:11:19.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, Kukaku…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.63,0:11:22.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I have a favor to ask of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.50,0:11:26.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's usually the case\Nwhen you look me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.40,0:11:32.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Is it a difficult problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.24,0:11:34.69,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Most likely.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.13,0:11:38.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a long time\Nsince we've talked like this…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.01,0:11:44.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,All right. Tell me,\NI love difficult things.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.98,0:12:32.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Can you see it, Rukia?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.87,0:12:34.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,From that window over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.13,0:12:37.62,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The two tools which will\Nbe used for your execution.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.05,0:12:39.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That is the Sokyoku.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.45,0:12:46.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A prisoner who is held in this tower
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.35,0:12:50.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,can look out the window that\Nhas been placed in the tower,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.71,0:12:53.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,and gaze out at the Sokyoku\Nand repent his sins.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.53,0:12:58.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That is why this is called\Nthe Repentance Cell.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.86,0:13:04.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Your hands…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.50,0:13:06.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Release!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.04,0:13:26.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for transferring\Nthe prisoner here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.82,0:13:28.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Let us go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.50,0:13:29.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.25,0:13:35.04,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Lieutenant Abarai…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.15,0:13:35.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.15,0:13:47.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Lieutenant!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.24,0:13:55.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Here is unconfirmed information:
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.24,0:14:00.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You already heard that there were\NRyoka in Soul Society yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.76,0:14:01.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Five of them…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.18,0:14:05.69,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And one of them wielded\Na sword as long as his body.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.91,0:14:08.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A Soul Reaper with orange-colored hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.10,0:14:10.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.30,0:14:15.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I see… I get the picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.24,0:14:24.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,All right, I'll take on the job.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.33,0:14:25.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.64,0:14:26.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.79,0:14:30.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If Urahara is involved,\NI can't refuse even if I wanted to.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.76,0:14:37.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,However, while I trust you…\NI don't trust those kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.45,0:14:42.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'll include my henchman\Nto keep an eye on them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.71,0:14:43.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Henchman?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.80,0:14:47.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Henchman,\Nbut he's actually my kid brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.29,0:14:51.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He's still a brat and not that useful.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.54,0:14:54.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.24,0:14:56.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh…just a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.24,0:14:58.33,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm opening the door, so behave!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.33,0:14:59.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.70,0:15:05.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,How do you do?!\NMy name is Ganju Shiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.47,0:15:07.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Please be good to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.54,0:15:24.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What? You know each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.54,0:15:34.94,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,How many days has it been since\NI saw her face looking so alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.01,0:15:40.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ichimaru was the one who\Nconfronted them,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.83,0:15:43.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,so that kid probably isn't alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.50,0:15:44.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.24,0:15:48.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I was probably right not to tell her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.86,0:15:50.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.70,0:15:51.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.50,0:15:55.06,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, it's been awhile, Abarai.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.53,0:15:56.77,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Aizen-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.08,0:16:00.73,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Can you talk?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.77,0:16:03.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Well…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.18,0:16:07.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's been quite some time\Nsince we talked like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.57,0:16:08.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.69,0:16:12.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Since you were sent to\NKenpachi's place.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.74,0:16:14.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,How many years has it been?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.25,0:16:17.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're with the Squad 6 now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.34,0:16:20.99,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Err…what did you want to\Ntalk to me about?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.65,0:16:35.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Abarai, you and her…\Nyou were close to Rukia Kuchiki, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.40,0:16:38.69,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't deny it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.45,0:16:42.87,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I heard you were\Nchums from the old days in Rukon District.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.15,0:16:43.91,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.91,0:16:46.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I won't waste any time then.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.33,0:16:53.12,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,In your eyes, should she die?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.17,0:16:59.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No… I don't understand\Nyour question.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.26,0:17:00.77,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think it's strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.17,0:17:05.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Her crime was the unauthorized transfer,\Nand loss, of her spiritual energy,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.64,0:17:07.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,and staying longer than allowed outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.45,0:17:12.27,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Certainly, heavy crimes,\Nbut the problem is how to deal with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.99,0:17:15.91,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The order for immediate return\Nand disposal of her Gigai.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.87,0:17:20.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The lessening of the grace period\Nfrom 35 days to 25 days,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.25,0:17:24.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,and the use of the Sokyoku on\None who is ranked below a captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.54,0:17:27.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,They're all outside the norm.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.50,0:17:33.33,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I have a feeling that this\Nis the will of one person.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.60,0:17:36.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it, Captain.\NWhat do you mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.49,0:17:37.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I have a bad feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.00,0:17:42.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Abarai, I may…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.35,0:17:47.91,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Attention all captains!\NAttention all captains!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.29,0:17:52.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,An urgent meeting will\Nnow be held! Repeat!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.32,0:18:01.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why you---!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.79,0:18:08.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hah! Serves you right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.75,0:18:09.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.96,0:18:10.73,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What--?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.02,0:18:19.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why you--!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.16,0:18:21.79,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,How's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.79,0:18:23.11,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Now I'm mad!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.39,0:18:24.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.65,0:18:48.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why you--!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.29,0:19:14.08,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Did she have to go that\Nfar to stop them?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.25,0:19:18.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I think I know why she always moves.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.45,0:19:20.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It must be hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.84,0:19:22.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's with you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.63,0:19:25.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Fighting from the minute you\Nset eyes on each other…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.03,0:19:26.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you know it's dangerous?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.38,0:19:28.60,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You destroyed my house!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.60,0:19:29.66,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.03,0:19:31.06,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But Sis...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.06,0:19:32.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No excuses!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.67,0:19:35.12,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Any complaints?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.10,0:19:37.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Err…no!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.10,0:19:37.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.43,0:19:41.79,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's with this?\NBoth brother and sister…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.95,0:19:43.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.65,0:19:52.83,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.07,0:19:54.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This is my house!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.30,0:19:58.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If you have a problem about\Nthe way I do things, get outta here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.34,0:20:01.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.77,0:20:04.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. As long as you understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.58,0:20:12.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Your sister is something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.40,0:20:13.33,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.92,0:20:15.89,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,All right. Everyone, stand!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.89,0:20:17.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.89,0:20:17.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.24,0:20:20.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Koganehiko, go outside with\NShiroganehiko and start the preparations.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.50,0:20:21.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.72,0:20:24.57,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The rest, be quiet and follow me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.79,0:20:30.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wow…why is there light\Nwhen we're underground?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.25,0:20:32.11,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't see any generators.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.34,0:20:34.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I keep hotaru-kazura in the\Nceiling cracks and
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.32,0:20:37.37,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,on both sides of the wooden frames.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.66,0:20:39.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hotaru-kazura?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.24,0:20:42.08,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Is that a plant or something that\Nis only found in Soul Society?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.54,0:20:46.23,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We're here. This is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.35,0:20:47.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Um…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.54,0:20:48.83,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Open it, Ganju.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.83,0:20:49.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.69,0:20:52.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Umm…!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.00,0:20:56.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's the big idea?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.28,0:20:58.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't defy her! Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.76,0:21:00.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Heave!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.47,0:21:12.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,W-What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.71,0:21:13.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.98,0:21:21.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'll shoot you guys into\NSeireitei with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.41,0:21:23.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,From the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.84,0:21:25.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sky?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.84,0:21:25.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sky?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.33,0:21:31.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Kukaku Shiba.\NI'm the best pyrotechnic in Rukongai!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.56,0:21:46.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,With much appreciation
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.44,0:21:48.73,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,send a rhapsody filled\Nwith treasured thoughts
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.77,0:21:52.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,To the people who have\Nalways held me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.19,0:21:54.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for everything
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.35,0:21:56.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.39,0:21:58.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wherever I may be
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.39,0:22:00.69,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll always be grateful for who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.48,0:22:03.69,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I was casually walking through town
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.73,0:22:05.77,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Around the time dusk fell\Nand the city was bathed in red
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.81,0:22:07.98,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It was an afternoon with\Ncrowds of people coming and going
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.02,0:22:09.77,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t know why but\NI just stood there and watched
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.81,0:22:12.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Then my cell phone started to vibrate\Nand I made myself move
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.39,0:22:14.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,hoping it could fill\Nin this hole in my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.39,0:22:16.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You’re not alone\NYou see, everybody
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.52,0:22:18.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We gotta hold each other up
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.56,0:22:20.85,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,With much appreciation
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.90,0:22:23.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I send a rhapsody filled\Nwith treasured thoughts
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.23,0:22:26.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,To the people who have\Nalways held me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.35,0:22:28.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for everything
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.39,0:22:30.52,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.56,0:22:32.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wherever I may be
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.48,0:22:34.73,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll always be grateful for who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.66,0:22:37.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This is the Special Hard\NSpiritual Partition Penetration Device
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.29,0:22:39.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,which my sister invented that can\Nbreak through the barrier
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.63,0:22:41.57,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,which surrounds the entire Seireitei
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.57,0:22:43.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,and which is made\Nfrom the Sekki-Seki
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.97,0:22:46.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,which breaks down\Nspiritual energy completely.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.37,0:22:48.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... Can you repeat that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.75,0:22:49.81,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Forget it!